Victorville.KATJ-FM: KATJ-FM is a commercial radio station in Victorville, California, broadcasting to the Victor Valley, California, area on 100.7 FM. It is the High Desert's only live country station. The official city of license is George, referring to George Air Force Base, which at its 1989 sign-on was an active military base and census-designated place. It was decommissioned in 1992 and later annexed by the city of Victorville.
